text.text: Where can I find the Waystar Submission page in ZOLL Billing?

text: To find the Waystar Submission page, you can hover over the Claims tab on the navigation bar and click Waystar Submission. This page allows you to send all queued claims to the clearinghouse at the push of a button instead of waiting for the nightly scheduled delivery.

text: To find the Waystar Submission page, you can hover over the Claims tab on the navigation bar and click Waystar Submission. This page allows you to send all queued claims to the clearinghouse at the push of a button instead of waiting for the nightly scheduled delivery.

text.text: What is the purpose of the Waystar Submission page?

text: The Waystar Submission page allows you to send all queued claims to the clearinghouse at the push of a button instead of waiting for the nightly scheduled delivery. To start, hover over Claims on the navigation bar and click Waystar Submission. Note: The table shows all the claims in the system, not just those scheduled for delivery.

text.text: Are there any specific permissions required to access and use the Waystar Submission feature?

text: The Waystar Submission feature is available to Customer Admins.
